@DATABASE "I, Ball"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - I - I, Ball"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - I
                   ====================================

                                  I, Ball
                                  =======


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49165,0)"}          49165,0
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49483,0)"}          49483,0
@{"No Enemies    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49714,33)"}          49714,33
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49781,58)"}          49781,58
@{"No weapon loss" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49017,33)"}          49017,33
@{"Time = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(52634,255)"}          52634,x (x=1 - 255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         "Time = x" is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
